{"tid":2291940,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"FA表明身份仍被捕 兩速龍稱「聽不到」","createTime":"2020-11-19T06:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T06:39:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e326e930fd0d665a9d05eff85d8cdc4e605262d3","tid":2291940,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:32:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201119/W7WJXQ7BLRC3VFPWYTO7D5ZPSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201119%2FW7WJXQ7BLRC3VFPWYTO7D5ZPSM%2F&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5gxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=9ecb1f6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201119%2FW7WJXQ7BLRC3VFPWYTO7D5ZPSM%2F&h=59967526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201119/W7WJXQ7BLRC3VFPWYTO7D5ZPSM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nFA表明身份仍被捕 兩速龍稱「聽不到」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/alLOP6fACjuIL7XQNEOtYKAJACY=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RSQILVIUCVAUXNLGKK7O3WOUCU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FalLOP6fACjuIL7XQNEOtYKAJACY%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRSQILVIUCVAUXNLGKK7O3WOUCU.jpg&h=2909856c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員林上嵐<br />\n<br />\n【8.31暴動案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年8月31日港島區遊行演變成警民衝突，在銅鑼灣被捕的七人被控暴動罪。辯方昨日播放案發新聞片段，顯示案中其中一名被告被速龍撲倒後高呼「我係first-aider」、旁觀人士亦提醒警員謂「急救員嚟㗎」。惟拘捕被告的兩名速龍均聲稱現場沒聽到有人自稱急救員，另外一名速龍則確認曾依被告要求幫他取出哮喘藥。<br />\n<br />\n反恐特勤隊警員張子杰供稱，當日協助同袍在珠城大廈捉住一名黑衣男、即本案首被告陳佐豪（25歲）。張去年10月為事件錄口供，開審前數周補錄新供詞，將案發地點「怡和街」改成「百德新街」，另將「皇室堡」改成「翡翠明珠廣場」，他解釋因對地點完全不熟悉，「其後有刑事部嘅同事問我，係咪地址上有些少出錯」才知悉有誤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n庭上播片「聽到類似聲音」<br />\n<br />\n辯方又播放新聞片段，顯。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n被三名速龍制服的首被告多次高呼「我係first-aider」等語句。<span class=\"orange\">張昨指現場沒聽到，而庭上播片則「聽到類似聲音」</span>。張稱：「你出現喺現場，着到咁嘅樣，你話你係first-aid，我都唔相信你係啦！」他對警方搜出首被告有六卷繃帶、生理鹽水等物品一概不知。<br />\n<br />\n同日在灣仔拘捕社工陳虹秀、。。。。。。。。。。，但沒留意他身上是否有其他急救用品。審訊周五續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC9/20<br />\n<br />\n===========<br />\n<br />\n蓄意扮聾<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">蓄聾</span>"},{"pid":"b9429087c18f1ecb7ac2a0fbeb5a99d1fd762c7f","tid":2291940,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:32:57.000Z","msg":"蓄意扮聾<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">蓄聾</span>"},{"pid":"792f9bd403dbbfa63fcb8451725524b272fc11bf","tid":2291940,"uid":373783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:35:51.000Z","msg":"兩條蟲聾, 乜都聽唔到,"},{"pid":"add139a386aa861f4503a7a8dfa8f12d5124562c","tid":2291940,"uid":191453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tuV732x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtuV732x.jpg&h=2f07bd28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n耳仔包到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點聽jack"}],"pinned":{"pid":"b9429087c18f1ecb7ac2a0fbeb5a99d1fd762c7f","tid":2291940,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:32:57.000Z","msg":"蓄意扮聾<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">蓄聾</span>"}}